      <title>纳格尔称，数字欧元的持有上限尚无定论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/nagel-says-jury-still-out-on-holding-limit-for-digital-euro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行行长约阿希姆·纳格尔 (Joachim Nagel) 表示，目前尚不清楚消费者对潜在数字欧元的持有限额应该是多少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/nagel-says-jury-still-out-on-holding-limit-for-digital-euro</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
