      <title>瑞银的福勒表示，市场对法国大选的反应似乎有些过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/ubs-fowler-overreaction-to-french-election-overdone-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银首席欧洲股票策略师兼衍生品主管 Gerry Fowler 表示，市场对法国大选的过度反应（提高欧洲风险溢价）似乎有些过头了。他在彭博简报中与 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/ubs-fowler-overreaction-to-french-election-overdone-video</guid>
